text: Rebecca "Nini" Alcantara Ynares (born September 26, 1949) is a Filipina politician from the province of Rizal, Philippines. She was first elected as governor of the province in 2001 and was re-elected in 2013 after the two terms of her spouse Casimiro Ynares Jr., and the single term of her son Casimiro Ynares III. Ynares won a second term in 2016 and a third term in 2019. On March 25, 2020, Ynares tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Rizal Official Website Category:Living people Category:Governors of Rizal Category:Filipino women in politics Category:Women provincial governors of the Philippines Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
